{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"CSS 数値ファクトリー関数","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSS/factory_functions","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"notecard experimental\" id=\"sect1\"><p><strong>Experimental:</strong> <strong>これは<a href=\"/ja/docs/MDN/Writing_guidelines/Experimental_deprecated_obsolete#experimental\">実験的な機能</a>です。</strong><br>本番で使用する前に<a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">ブラウザー互換性一覧表</a>をチェックしてください。</p></div>\n<p><strong>CSS 数値ファクトリー関数</strong>、たとえば <code>CSS.em()</code> や <code>CSS.turn()</code> は、値を数値引数、単位を使用するメソッド名として <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSUnitValue\">CSSUnitValues</a> を返すもので、このメソッドを使用すると、数値引数で単位を設定することができます。これらの関数は <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSUnitValue/CSSUnitValue\"><code>CSSUnitValue()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> コンストラクターを使うよりも冗長でなく新しい数値を生成します。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"構文","title":"構文","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token constant\">CSS</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">number</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>number<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token constant\">CSS</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">percent</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>number<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// &lt;length&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"token constant\">CSS</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">em</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>number<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token constant\">CSS</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">ex</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>number<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token constant\">CSS</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">ch</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>number<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token constant\">CSS</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">ic</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>number<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token constant\">CSS</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">rem</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>number<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token constant\">CSS</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">lh</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>number<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token constant\">CSS</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">rlh</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>number<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token constant\">CSS</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">vw</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>number<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token constant\">CSS</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">vh</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>number<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token constant\">CSS</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">vi</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>number<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token constant\">CSS</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">vb</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>number<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token constant\">CSS</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">vmin</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>number<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token constant\">CSS</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">vmax</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>number<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token constant\">CSS</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">cm</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>number<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token constant\">CSS</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">mm</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>number<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token constant\">CSS</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token constant\">Q</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>number<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token constant\">CSS</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">in</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>number<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token constant\">CSS</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">pt</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>number<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token constant\">CSS</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">pc</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>number<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token constant\">CSS</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">px</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>number<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// &lt;angle&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"token constant\">CSS</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">deg</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>number<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token constant\">CSS</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">grad</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>number<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token constant\">CSS</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">rad</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>number<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token constant\">CSS</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">turn</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>number<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// &lt;time&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"token constant\">CSS</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">s</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>number<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token constant\">CSS</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">ms</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>number<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// &lt;frequency&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"token constant\">CSS</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">Hz</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>number<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token constant\">CSS</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">kHz</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>number<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// &lt;resolution&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"token constant\">CSS</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">dpi</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>number<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token constant\">CSS</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">dpcm</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>number<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token constant\">CSS</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">dppx</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>number<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// &lt;flex&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"token constant\">CSS</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">fr</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>number<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"例","title":"例","isH3":false,"content":"<p>数値ファクトリー関数の <code>CSS.vmax()</code> を使用して <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSUnitValue\"><code>CSSUnitValue</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> を作成します。</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> height <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token constant\">CSS</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">vmax</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">50</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span> height <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>       <span class=\"token comment\">// CSSUnitValue {value: 50, unit: \"vmax\"}</span>\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span> height<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>value <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>  <span class=\"token comment\">// 50</span>\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span> height<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>unit <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>   <span class=\"token comment\">// vmax</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>この例では、要素のマージンを <code>CSS.px()</code> ファクトリー関数で設定します。</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>myElement<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>attributeStyleMap<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">set</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'margin'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token constant\">CSS</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">px</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">40</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> currentMargin <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> myElement<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>attributeStyleMap<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">get</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'margin'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>currentMargin<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>value<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> currentMargin<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>unit<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 40, 'px'</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"仕様書","id":"仕様書","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://drafts.csswg.org/cssom/#namespacedef-css","title":"CSS Object Model (CSSOM)"}],"query":"api.CSS"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"ブラウザーの互換性","isH3":false,"query":"api.CSS","dataURL":"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSS/factory_functions/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"関連情報","title":"関連情報","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSUnitValue/CSSUnitValue\"><code>CSSUnitValue()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"構文","id":"構文"},{"text":"例","id":"例"},{"text":"仕様書","id":"仕様書"},{"text":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"ブラウザーの互換性"},{"text":"関連情報","id":"関連情報"}],"summary":"CSS 数値ファクトリー関数、たとえば CSS.em() や CSS.turn() は、値を数値引数、単位を使用するメソッド名として CSSUnitValues を返すもので、このメソッドを使用すると、数値引数で単位を設定することができます。これらの関数は CSSUnitValue() (en-US) コンストラクターを使うよりも冗長でなく新しい数値を生成します。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"CSS numeric factory functions","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"CSS 数字工厂函数","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/api/css/factory_functions","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/api/css/factory_functions/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web","title":"開発者向けのウェブ技術"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSS","title":"CSS"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSS/factory_functions","title":"CSS 数値ファクトリー関数"}],"pageTitle":"CSS 数値ファクトリー関数 - Web API | MDN","noIndexing":false}}